<li><a href="/wiki/Macgregor%27s_Bowerbird" title="Macgregor's Bowerbird">Macgregor's Bowerbird</a>, <i>Amblyornis macgregoriae</i></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Streaked_Bowerbird" title="Streaked Bowerbird">Streaked Bowerbird</a>, <i>Amblyornis subalaris</i></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Golden-fronted_Bowerbird" title="Golden-fronted Bowerbird">Golden-fronted Bowerbird</a>, <i>Amblyornis flavifrons</i></li>
</ul>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:244px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Prionodura_newtoniana_by_Bowdler_Sharpe.jpg" class="image" title="Golden Bowerbird male (top) and female"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/37/Prionodura_newtoniana_by_Bowdler_Sharpe.jpg/242px-Prionodura_newtoniana_by_Bowdler_Sharpe.jpg" width="242" height="293" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Prionodura_newtoniana_by_Bowdler_Sharpe.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
<a href="/wiki/Golden_Bowerbird" title="Golden Bowerbird">Golden Bowerbird</a> male (top) and female</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>Genus <i>Prionodura</i></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Golden_Bowerbird" title="Golden Bowerbird">Golden Bowerbird</a>, <i>Prionodura newtoniana</i></li>
</ul>
<p>Genus <i><a href="/wiki/Sericulus" title="Sericulus">Sericulus</a></i></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Flame_Bowerbird" title="Flame Bowerbird">Flame Bowerbird</a>, <i>Sericulus aureus</i></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Fire-maned_Bowerbird" title="Fire-maned Bowerbird">Fire-maned Bowerbird</a>, <i>Sericulus bakeri</i></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Regent_Bowerbird" title="Regent Bowerbird">Regent Bowerbird</a>, <i>Sericulus chrysocephalus</i></li>
</ul>
<p>Genus <i>Ptilonorhynchus</i></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Satin_Bowerbird" title="Satin Bowerbird">Satin Bowerbird</a>, <i>Ptilonorhynchus violaceus</i></li>
</ul>
<p>Genus <i><a href="/wiki/Chlamydera" title="Chlamydera">Chlamydera</a></i></p>
<p>Note that the <a href="/wiki/Gray_Catbird" title="Gray Catbird">Gray Catbird</a> (<i>Dumetella carolinensis</i>) and <a href="/wiki/Black_Catbird" title="Black Catbird">Black Catbird</a> (<i>Melanoptila glabrirostris</i>) from the <a href="/wiki/Americas" title="Americas">Americas</a> and the <a href="/wiki/Abyssinian_Catbird" title="Abyssinian Catbird">Abyssinian Catbird</a> (<i>Parophasma galinieri</i>) from <a href="/wiki/Africa" title="Africa">Africa</a> are unrelated birds that belong to different families.</p>
<p><a name="Distribution_and_habitat_2" id="Distribution_and_habitat_2"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Bowerbird&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: Distribution and habitat">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Distribution and habitat</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Western_Bowerbird" title="Western Bowerbird">Western Bowerbird</a>, <i>Chlamydera guttata</i></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Spotted_Bowerbird" title="Spotted Bowerbird">Spotted Bowerbird</a>, <i>Chlamydera maculata</i></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Great_Bowerbird" title="Great Bowerbird">Great Bowerbird</a>, <i>Chlamydera nuchalis</i></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Yellow-breasted_Bowerbird" title="Yellow-breasted Bowerbird">Yellow-breasted Bowerbird</a>, <i>Chlamydera lauterbachi</i></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Fawn-breasted_Bowerbird" title="Fawn-breasted Bowerbird">Fawn-breasted Bowerbird</a>, <i>Chlamydera cerviniventris</i></li>
</ul>
